body:
Using c++11 lambda here?

Something like:

``` c++
std::lower_bound(vChain.begin(), vChain.end(), nTime,
   [](CBlockIndex* pBlock, const int64_t& time) -> bool { return pBlock->GetBlockTime() < time; }
);
```

Would probably be less confusing to read.

