+            HelpExampleCli("importmulti", "'[{ \"scriptPubKey\": { \"address\": \"<my address>\" }, \"timestamp\":1455191478 }]' '{ \"rescan\": false}'") +
+
+            "\nResponse is an array with the same size as the input that has the execution result :\n"
